<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Analyse Tactique - Kaypic Photo</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css"> 
</head>
<body>
    <header class="project-detail-header" style="text-align: center;">
        <div class="score-board">
            <span class="status-live">● PROJET TERMINÉ</span>
            <h1>Kaypic Photo</h1>
            <p class="tagline">Gestion de prestations et galeries événementielles</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="projets-section">
        <section class="project-gallery">
                <h3>Aperçu de l'application (Captures d'écran)</h3>
                <div class="gallery-grid">

                    <div class="screenshot-container">
                        <div class="screenshot-frame">
                            <%= image_tag "kaypic/Inscription_Kaypic.png", alt: "Aperçu", onclick: "openLightbox(this)", style: "cursor: zoom-in;" %>
                        </div>
                        <p class="screenshot-caption">Inscription à la plateforme</p>
                    </div>


                    
                    <div class="screenshot-container">
                        <div class="screenshot-frame">
                            <%= image_tag "kaypic/Accueil_Kaypic.png", alt: "Aperçu", onclick: "openLightbox(this)", style: "cursor: zoom-in;" %>
                        </div>
                        <p class="screenshot-caption">Page d'accueil de l'application</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="screenshot-container">
                        <div class="screenshot-frame">
                            <%= image_tag "kaypic/Explorer_Kaypic.png", alt: "Aperçu", onclick: "openLightbox(this)", style: "cursor: zoom-in;" %>
                        </div>
                        <p class="screenshot-caption">Mode explorer de toutes les photos disponibles sur la plateforme.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="screenshot-container">
                        <div class="screenshot-frame">
                            <%= image_tag "kaypic/Mes_Albums_Kaypic.png", alt: "Aperçu", onclick: "openLightbox(this)", style: "cursor: zoom-in;" %>
                        </div>
                        <p class="screenshot-caption">Mes albums</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="screenshot-container">
                        <div class="screenshot-frame">
                             <%= image_tag "kaypic/Album_Photo_Kaypic.png", alt: "Aperçu", onclick: "openLightbox(this)", style: "cursor: zoom-in;" %>
                        </div>
                        <p class="screenshot-caption">Liste des photos disponible dans un album.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="screenshot-container">
                        <div class="screenshot-frame">
                            <%= image_tag "kaypic/Annonces_Kaypic.png", alt: "Aperçu", onclick: "openLightbox(this)", style: "cursor: zoom-in;" %>
                        </div>
                        <p class="screenshot-caption">Annonces de disponibilités faites par des photographes.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="screenshot-container">
                        <div class="screenshot-frame">
                            <%= image_tag "kaypic/Gestion_Du_Compte_Kaypic.png", alt: "Aperçu", onclick: "openLightbox(this)", style: "cursor: zoom-in;" %>
                        </div>
                        <p class="screenshot-caption">Gestion de notre profil utilisateur</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="screenshot-container">
                        <div class="screenshot-frame">
                            <%= image_tag "kaypic/Messagerie_Kaypic.png", alt: "Aperçu", onclick: "openLightbox(this)", style: "cursor: zoom-in;" %>
                        </div>
                        <p class="screenshot-caption">Messagerie textuelle</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="screenshot-container">
                        <div class="screenshot-frame">
                            <%= image_tag "kaypic/Mon_Profil_Kaypic.png", alt: "Aperçu", onclick: "openLightbox(this)", style: "cursor: zoom-in;" %>
                        </div>
                        <p class="screenshot-caption">Détails de mon profil</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="screenshot-container">
                        <div class="screenshot-frame">
                            <%= image_tag "kaypic/Photographe_Profil_Kaypic.png", alt: "Aperçu", onclick: "openLightbox(this)", style: "cursor: zoom-in;" %>
                        </div>
                        <p class="screenshot-caption">Profil publique d'un photographe</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="screenshot-container">
                        <div class="screenshot-frame">
                            <%= image_tag "kaypic/Photographes_Kaypic.png", alt: "Aperçu", onclick: "openLightbox(this)", style: "cursor: zoom-in;" %>
                        </div>
                        <p class="screenshot-caption">Liste des photographes de la plateforme</p>
                    </div>

                </div> 
            </section>

        <div class="final-action" style="margin-top: 40px; text-align: center;">
            <a href="https://github.com/lucasbidaultmeresse/Kaypic-Photo" target="_blank" class="github-btn">
                <svg class="github-logo" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path d="M12 .297c-6.63 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.303 3.438 9.8 8.205 11.385.6.113.82-.258.82-.577 0-.285-.01-1.04-.015-2.04-3.338.724-4.042-1.61-4.042-1.61C4.422 18.07 3.633 17.7 3.633 17.7c-1.087-.744.084-.729.084-.729 1.205.084 1.838 1.236 1.838 1.236 1.07 1.835 2.809 1.305 3.495.998.108-.776.417-1.305.76-1.605-2.665-.3-5.466-1.332-5.466-5.93 0-1.31.465-2.38 1.235-3.22-.135-.303-.54-1.523.105-3.176 0 0 1.005-.322 3.3 1.23.96-.267 1.98-.399 3-.405 1.02.006 2.04.138 3 .405 2.28-1.552 3.285-1.23 3.285-1.23.645 1.653.24 2.873.12 3.176.765.84 1.23 1.91 1.23 3.22 0 4.61-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.92.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222 0 1.606-.015 2.896-.015 3.286 0 .315.21.69.825.57C20.565 22.092 24 17.592 24 12.297c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12"/>
                </svg>
                Consulter le code source
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="project-detail-container">
            <section class="detail-grid">
                <div class="detail-card">
                    <h3>Description du projet</h3>
                    <br>
                    <p>Module dédié aux photographes pour centraliser la gestion des événements duquel un professionnel souhaiterai simplifier pour gagner du temps et utiliser une interface conviviale. En effet la plateforme offres des services comme les réservations clients, la livraison de photos haute définition, la possibilité de faire des annonces, créer son propre portfolio de photographie ou gérer un vrai business afin d'exposer ses plus belles réalisations.</p>
                    <br>
                    <p>Projet fait en collaboration avec :</p>
                    <ul class="tech-list">
                        <li><strong>- Yudas Amer</strong></li>
                        <li><strong>- Sabourin Matthew</strong></li>
                        <li><strong>- Mathis Perreault</strong></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-card">
                    <h3>Dispositif Technique</h3>
                    <ul class="tech-list">
                        <li><strong>Framework :</strong> ASP.Net Core & Blazor</li>
                        <li><strong>Langage :</strong> C#, HTML, CSS, Javascript</li>
                        <li><strong>Base de données :</strong> SQL</li>
                        <li><strong>Frontend :</strong> Portfolio dynamique réactif</li>
                        <li><strong>Librairies :</strong> ASP.Net : SignalR, Identity, Core, Authorization</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="analysis-section">
                <h3>Quelques fonctionnalités incluses :</h3>
                <div class="analysis-grid">
                    <div class="analysis-item">
                        <h4>Média</h4>
                        <p>Optimisation de l'affichage des galeries haute définition à la manière d'un portfolio.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="analysis-item">
                        <h4>Réservation</h4>
                        <p>Système d'annonces et de contact entre les prestations d'un photographe et ses clients.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="analysis-item">
                        <h4>Expérience</h4>
                        <p>Interface intuitive pour la livraison de clichés après événement.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <div id="lightbox" class="lightbox" onclick="closeLightbox()">
        <span class="lightbox-close">&times;</span>
        <img id="lightbox-img" src="" alt="Agrandissement">
    </div>

    <script>
        function openLightbox(imgElement) {
            const lightbox = document.getElementById('lightbox');
            const lightboxImg = document.getElementById('lightbox-img');
            lightbox.style.display = 'flex';
            lightboxImg.src = imgElement.src;
        }
        function closeLightbox() {
            document.getElementById('lightbox').style.display = 'none';
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>